tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE DemandMetrics (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    product_id INT,
    demand_value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE sales_data (
    sale_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    sale_date DATE,
    quantity INT,
    total_price DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE Dashboard (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    category VARCHAR(50),
    description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Visualization (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dashboard_id INT,
    type VARCHAR(50),
    data_source VARCHAR(100),
    FOREIGN KEY (dashboard_id) REFERENCES Dashboard(id)
)

CREATE TABLE DemandFluctuations (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    demand INT,
    fluctuation DECIMAL(10,2),
    dashboard_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (dashboard_id) REFERENCES Dashboard(id)
)

CREATE TABLE UserSettings (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    dashboard_id INT,
    theme VARCHAR(50),
    timezone VARCHAR(50),
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES Users(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (dashboard_id) REFERENCES Dashboard(id)
)
